description:
&lt;p&gt;Following the departure of a long-serving Consultant we are looking for a full time Consultant Psychiatrist in General Adult Psychiatry, working in the Enfield North Locality Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role involves significant Mental Health Act work and you will act as a Responsible Clinician for patients under section in the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer community support and treatment to people with common mental health issue such as anxiety, depression, and schizophrenia, bi-polar affective disorder, psychotic depression and other psychiatric disorders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer a range of treatment and intervention services including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Specialised medical psychiatric treatment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Individual, group and family therapy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carer assessment and support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employment and education support with welfare advice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Community care assessments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Services will be offered to patients according to their needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is based at 58-60 Silver Street, Enfield, EN1 3EP.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Strictly no agencies please&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Pardeep Grewal, Interim Clinical Director, Enfield Mental Health Division&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;pardeepgrewal@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Matthew Liveras, Medical Lead, Enfield Mental Health Division&lt;/p&gt;
